1:30:18.500 --> 1:30:21.375
- Here you go.
- What am I supposed to do?

1:30:21.542 --> 1:30:26.542
- You'll do what you're told.
- Just keep your eyes and ears open.

1:30:28.083 --> 1:30:31.542
Remember the scent of eucalyptus?

