- A rich steward, as in Jack London.</i>

1:30:50.583 --> 1:30:53.292
<i>- Nothing's simple with you.
- Everything is.</i>

1:30:53.458 --> 1:30:55.542
<i>Too much happens at once.</i>

1:30:55.708 --> 1:31:00.292
<i>Here are two men who beat me up,
